Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.75,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どうして僕らは出逢ったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}数字なんかじゃ証明できない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:07.70,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どんな歴史も色褪せるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.13,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}神秘のディスカバリー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.91,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ピタリとハマった　天声のパスワード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.08,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}宇宙Levelのシンパシー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:24.93,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}創造紀元の胎動が聞こえているか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.51,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:31.29,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}極上の未来を作り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:38.20,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}争鳴の空へと飴色のジェットで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:43.33,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}未熟な夢積み込んだらフルスロットル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:50.30,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}翔ぼう！想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:02:00.27,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:54.25,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.75,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:07.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:24.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.51,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:31.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:38.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:43.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:50.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:02:00.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.28,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち止まらず 歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.49,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星を数えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:29.72,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消せない絆が 光るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:37.16,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夢は走り出した 僕らを導いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:41.53,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願いを込めて　描く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:46.75,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}守りたい 気持ちはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:52.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち向かう 勇気くれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.37,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まっすぐ伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.40,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌うよ　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.60,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けて　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:05.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘れない 胸の奥で 輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.24,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がくれた光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.25,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一緒に　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願うよ　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:18.25,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強く握りしめる手は 温かく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:23.70,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと 離さないよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.17,0:00:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.28,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.49,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就像在数着天上的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:29.72,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:37.16,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:41.53,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:46.75,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:52.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.37,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.40,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.60,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:05.81,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.24,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.25,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:18.25,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:23.70,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
